(TOOL CHANGER TEST PROGRAM)
((C) MICHAEL DILLIO FOR PRAXIS MECHATRONICS 2023)

(---------OPTIMIZED FOR HAAS NGC CONTROL-------)
(RUNS THROUGH ALL TOOLS IN THE TOOL CHANGER, TESTING FOR)
(ORIENTATION AND PROPER FUNCTIONING OF SMTC OR UMBRELLA.)
(#10001 IS THE CURRENT TOOL, #10002 IS A COUNTER OF TOTAL)
(TOOL CHANGES PERFORMED. #10003 STORES HOW MANY TOOLS AVAIL:)
(#10003 = 10 FOR A SMALL UMBRELLA, 40 FOR BIG SMTC, ETC.)


G103 P1



#10003 = 24 (TOTAL NUMBER OF TOOLS IN CAROUSEL)
#10002 = 1 {SET COUNTER TO 1)
N50 (OUTER LOOP START)
#10001 = 1 (SET INITIAL TOOL TO 1)
M97 P100 L99 (BEGIN INNER LOOP BY CALLING LINE 100)

GOTO200 (99 OUTER LOOPS COMPLETED)

N100 T#10001 M6
S200 M3
G4 P2.
#10002 = #10002 + 1 (INCREMENT COUNTER)
#10001 = #10001 + 1 (INCREMENT TOOL #)
IF [ #10001 GT #10003 ] GOTO50 (TEST FOR LAST TOOL)
(IF ALL TOOLS HAVE CHANGED, RESTART OUTER LOOP AT N50)
M99 (RETURN TO M97 LINE: CHANGE TO NEXT TOOL)
N200 G103 (RESUME LOOKAHEAD)
M30


